# Reflection Engine — PASS-010

Every project completion ends with structured reflection.

```txt
What happened? · What did you learn? · What should happen next?
```

## Loop

```txt
Goal → Path → Project → Action → Evidence → Reflection → Insight → Next Best Action
```

Without reflection, Foundry knows what people did — not what they learned.

Do not build project completion without reflection hooks.

`REFLECTION_TEMPLATES` in `@foundry/reflection-engine`

See `docs/REFLECTION_ENGINE.md`
